Package wahoot.db.models

Class Student

java.lang.Object
wahoot.db.models.User
wahoot.db.models.Student
@Entity(name="Student") public final class Student extends User
Represents a student entity in the system. A student is a type of user that can be enrolled in multiple classrooms and belongs to a specific school. This class extends the User class, inheriting user properties such as firstname, lastname, username, email, and password.
